- `RE_GITHUB_REPO` (line 1304): pattern `[a-z0-9-]+/[a-z0-9._-]+` matches "key/value", "path/to" (first segment only), ISO date "2024-01" with any suffix. False positives expected in practice. Risk: low-signal noise in KG.
