### Tool Surface Inventory

| Tool name | Handler | Required args | Optional args | Return shape |
|-----------|---------|---------------|---------------|-------------|
| `search_person_conversations` | `search_person_conversations()` | person, query | limit (int, default 10, max 50), platform (enum) | person{}, query, count, results[], platform_errors[]? |
